"...The TFLN platform incorporates topological photonic crystals to create protected edge-state waveguides. These structures provide backscattering-immune light propagation that is inherently robust against defects and disorder (as demonstrated", "id_str": "2074555776899719638", "in_reply_to_screen_name": "n_gregory79574", "in_reply_to_status_id_str": "2074554078269747695", "in_reply_to_user_id_str": "2021617839782985729", "is_quote_status": false, "lang": "en", "quote_count": 0, "reply_count": 0, "retweet_count": 0, "retweeted": false, "user_id_str": "2021617839782985729"}, "note_tweet": {"is_expandable": true, "note_tweet_results": {"result": {"entity_set": {"hashtags": [], "symbols": [], "urls": [], "user_mentions": []}, "id": "Tm90ZVR3ZWV0OjIwNzQ1NTU3NzY4MTU4Mjg5OTI=", "text": "If you build it they won't come!

"...The TFLN platform incorporates topological photonic crystals to create protected edge-state waveguides. These structures provide backscattering-immune light propagation that is inherently robust against defects and disorder (as demonstrated in topological photonics literature). This physical-layer protection complements the system-level topological surplus generated via Artin braid inversion, resulting in multi-layered resilience.""}}}, "rest_id": "2074555776899719638", "source": "<a href="http://twitter.com/download/android" rel="nofollow">Twitter for Android</a>", "unmention_data": {}, "views": {"count": "20", "state": "EnabledWithCount"}}

