text:
@aleabitoreddit SemiAnalysis's June report flagged CPO yield/delay concerns, pressuring photonics stocks like $HIMX &amp; $LITE. 

Shortly after, Semi partnered with Tema on the LAZR Photonics ETF, holding those names. 

The whole situation is questionable.

